nodes.text: Gadrin Spaceport was a spaceport that was located in the city Gadrin on the planet Cularin. During the time of the Clone Wars, the Gran Nadin Paal maintained a warehouse in Docking Bay 77 of the spaceport. Following the return of the Hutt crime lord Riboga to the Cularin system, the assassin Kills traveled to the spaceport and attempted to murder Paal.
